What Einstein showed is things that Newton thought were certain, absolute space and time,

49:19.660 --> 49:26.100
these kinds of formula, actually don't possess the certainty that Newton thought they did.

49:26.100 --> 49:36.220
We'll talk a little bit later about why we can't accept in very limited context.

49:36.220 --> 49:41.460
There are deep, deep reasons why we can't pursue certainty.

49:41.460 --> 49:50.120
And therefore we can't seek certainty as a solution to loss of connection, connection

49:50.120 --> 49:54.400
to our self, connection to the world, connection to other minds.

