attempt to address this burgeoning loss of connections?

50:10.720 --> 50:17.300
What does it actually result in exactly the opposite, increased sense of disconnectedness?

50:17.300 --> 50:23.140
Part of it, of course, is the failure of the project of certainty.

50:23.140 --> 50:33.340
You can understand the 18th and the 19th, and especially the 20th centuries as scientific,

50:33.340 --> 50:40.280
historical, and philosophical undermining of the idea that we can achieve certainty.

50:40.280 --> 50:51.280
Of course, one of the great principles of modern physics is the uncertainty principle.

50:51.280 --> 50:52.280
But let's go back.

