So matter is inert, it's resistance, it's really there, I push on it.

52:43.960 --> 52:51.600
Notice that again, all that's left of conformity is resistance of will.

52:51.600 --> 53:12.220
Hobbes says, well, matter is real, and what if I built a material machine

53:12.220 --> 53:20.500
that did computation?

53:20.500 --> 53:26.120
