Right there, at the heart of the scientific revolution, Hobbes is proposing artificial

53:48.320 --> 53:52.020
intelligence.

53:52.020 --> 54:07.740
Notice how artificial intelligence is a child of the advent of the meaning crisis and the

54:07.740 --> 54:08.900
scientific revolution.

54:08.900 --> 54:11.740
It's not a modern idea.

54:11.740 --> 54:16.100
Artificial intelligence goes back to this time.

54:16.480 --> 54:21.720
What is Hobbes doing with this?

54:21.720 --> 54:30.000
I said Galileo kills the universe and Copernicus kills the reality of our sense experience,

54:30.000 --> 54:36.960
but Hobbes is doing something way more personal because up till now, you've been isolated

54:36.960 --> 54:40.760
inside your own mind, but at least still there.

54:40.760 --> 54:46.080
