54:46.100 --> 54:54.620
Hobbes kills the soul, no soul, because if artificial intelligence is right, if I can

54:54.620 --> 55:00.820
build a machine, purely material machine that is capable of computation, then I will have

55:00.820 --> 55:11.580
made a mind and I didn't have to involve any soul stuff, any spirit stuff in making it.

55:11.580 --> 55:13.580
And that's radical.

55:13.600 --> 55:20.360
Take a look at how Descartes responds to that and how deep that response is woven into our

55:20.360 --> 55:30.000
culture and the meaning crisis and how we move between AI and Descartes even today.

